The,Consumer,Insights,API,allows,for,easy,integration,of,real,time,social,insights,into,other,business,applications,to,enrich,contact,and,profile,data,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON,LeadSift,is,a,social,intelligence,platform,that,mines,audiences,to,help,brands,identify,understand,and,reach,consumers,in,real,time,through,the,lens,of,intent,profile,and,affinity,For,every,user,collected,over,attributes,about,their,habits,trends,preferences,and,lifestyle,are,extracted,and,analyzed,to,create,a,degree,view,of,a,customer